{"tid":1105301,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"手汗多點算好？","createTime":"2019-04-13T18:35:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-16T20:19:22.000Z","uid":225403,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"2e4ba04321eb87b3fc995ad8e67466adb0ee870d","tid":1105301,"uid":225403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T18:35:32.000Z","msg":"自己對手經常都出汗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有時仲多到滴得出水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n特別係考試，拎到枝筆濕曬，有時張卷都會濕埋<br />\n中學果時又試過上台領獎同校長握手，多手汗到校長問我點解咁多手汗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好柒<br />\n過e道又過唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />用iphone又用唔到指紋開鎖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用衫用紙巾都抹唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />永遠都keep住咁濕<br />\n究竟點算好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"069d8bcb2242ac7bfb7f9a20160e231cae94d5c3","tid":1105301,"uid":191300,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T18:43:42.000Z","msg":"加一 <br />\n我成日洗手都無乜用<br />\n係可以唔夠一分鐘又出汗<br />\n無誇張到<br />\n<br />\nBtw有啲減汗線嘅手術做"},{"pid":"ce26c786847a9cf5ee75e686d052ae35e407e883","tid":1105301,"uid":181581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T18:54:14.000Z","msg":"試下用odaban<br />\n見有啲人用完有效"},{"pid":"e48015ab732039a855ee493c85273af2ea979257","tid":1105301,"uid":23757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce26c786847a9cf5ee75e686d052ae35e407e883","tid":1105301,"uid":181581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T18:54:14.000Z","msg":"試下用odaban<br />\n見有啲人用完有效"},"citedBy":1,"rep